Class AxisLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • oscilloscup.system.SpaceElement
      • oscilloscup.system.BoundedSpaceElement
        • oscilloscup.system.AxisLine

  • public class AxisLine
extends BoundedSpaceElement

    The axis line belong to an axis. The bounds of the line may differ from the bounds of the parent axis.

    On the upper bound of the line is drawn an arrow.
